[Hranica Guanling, Qianzhou]

535
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:25,009
[Hranica Guanling, Qianzhou]

536
00:34:25,010 --> 00:34:27,499
Vaša výsosť, dorazili sme na hranicu Guanlingu.

537
00:34:27,499 --> 00:34:29,740
